msgctxt "f3cc"
msgid ""
"We would like to show you content from the provider {title}, but respect "
"your privacy. If you agree to the {link_start}provider’s privacy "
"policy{link_end}, please click the following button to view the content."
msgstr ""
"Nus vulain mussar a Vus cuntegns dal purschider {title}, ma respectar Vossa "
"sfera privata. Sche Vus essas d’accord cun la {link_start}decleraziun da "
"protecziun da datas da l’offerent{link_end}, cliccai sin il suandant buttun "
"per inditgar il cuntegn."

