"We use cookies to enhance the user experience on our website. Read our "
"{link_start}privacy policy{link_end} to find out more about how we use "
"cookies and protect your data."
msgstr ""
"Nus utilisain cookies per porscher ina pagina-web pratica per las "
"utilisadras ed ils utilisaders. En nossa {link_start}directiva davart la "
"protecziun da datas{link_end} chattais Vus ulteriuras infurmaziuns co che "
"nus faschain diever da cookies e protegin Vossas datas."

